        "en_title": "Several people taken hostage in a cafe in Holland",
        "en_content": "Several people were taken\nhostage in a cafe in the Dutch city of Ede. It refers\nthe police, who is evacuating the houses near the\nLocal. According to local media, the kidnapping author would have\nSaid he was in possession of explosive devices.\nThe Dutch police said on X that \"at the moment\" there is no\nstill no sign of \"terroristic motion\" in the grip of\nhostages in Ede where several people were seized in a\nCoffee.\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
